{% # Preload hints v1.0.0 %}

{% doc %}
  @description Renders <link rel="preload"> / <link rel="preconnect"> / <link rel="dns-prefetch"> hints for critical-path resources.

  Add a hint here when a resource is:
  - Needed before the renderer discovers it in CSS/JS (fonts referenced from CSS, hero images, etc.)
  - Hosted on a third-party origin whose TCP/TLS handshake is worth starting early (preconnect)

  Skip when:
  - The resource is inlined
  - Shopify's CDN already handles it

  @example {% render 'utility--preload-hints' %}
{% enddoc %}
